response.overview: On March 2nd GCW presents Keep in Touch 2024 live on TrillerTV+ straight from Indianapolis Marriott East. The event features the GCW World Title Match where Blake Christian defends his title against Arik Cannon.  Also in the lineup:  Steph De Lander vs Sawyer Wreck  Myron Reed vs Jack Cartwheel  Billy Roc vs Billie Starkz  Calvin Tankman vs Alex Zayne  GCW Tag Team Title Match  Violence Is Forever (Dominic Garrini & Kevin Ku) vs Gahbage Daddies (Alec Price & Cole Radrick)  Nate Webb vs Mance Warner  Tag Team Match  The Rejects (John Wayne Murdoch & Reed Bentley) vs Maki Death Kill (Maki Itoh & Nick Gage)
response.title: GCW Keep in Touch 2024
